{"tid":2518086,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【估地方】9歲童上堂傾偈 竟遭扯髮致「骨肉分離」 穿刺治療哭喊片睇到心悒","createTime":"2021-05-05T20:04:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T20:48:40.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c8e7e94ace639e9e977190771ac68529f60079d6","tid":2518086,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T20:04:58.000Z","msg":"河南有網民日前爆料，指平頂山市一名9歲苑姓男童，今年3月因在課堂上與同學說話，遭冷血的常姓男教師強扯頭髮。男童回家後感到惡心嘔吐，家長發現他頭部腫脹，即帶他到醫院檢查，結果竟發現他因大面積頭髮被用力拉扯，頭皮與頭骨已經「骨肉分離」，中間積血，必須透過穿刺抽出血液，才能讓頭皮與頭骨重新貼合，正常生長。男童治療時發出撕心裂肺哭喊聲的影片流出後，激起網民熱議。警方於5月1日發出的鑑定意見通知書顯示，男童屬輕傷二級；目前，常男已被刑事拘留。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210506/A4DIYZTPPFH3DK4F4HQSHPTT7Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210506%2FA4DIYZTPPFH3DK4F4HQSHPTT7Q%2F&d=lnSleIYCVJUMUgC9CFuHQilZyh30VB0jKt3ffwT98zY%3D&h=5543c27b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210506%2FA4DIYZTPPFH3DK4F4HQSHPTT7Q%2F&h=9b353d1c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210506/A4DIYZTPPFH3DK4F4HQSHPTT7Q/</a>"},{"pid":"1b7b6fedbde02712fc8fe8248fc7958b92bfa02e","tid":2518086,"uid":329733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T20:11:28.000Z","msg":"鬼國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfd97006fe2f75c19fa0e96ef73ebff8de1d65dd","tid":2518086,"uid":329733,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T20:12:13.000Z","msg":"個細路唔好彩<br />\n搞到咁痛苦都冇首抽重刷嘅機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im